    • getButtonBox

      @NotNull public @NotNull javafx.scene.layout.VBox getButtonBox()

      Returns the VBox container housing all selection buttons mapped to all UIBooks in this SidebarBookshelf.

      Details

      1. The VBox returned by this method is created automatically in the SidebarBookshelf constructor.

      Usage in Sidebar

      1. The Sidebar class automatically sets the button box that is displayed on the UI at any given time to always reflect the selected SidebarBookshelf.
      2. Therefore, the parent of the VBox returned by this method must never be directly modified, changed, or otherwise manipulated.
      3. This method previously had protected access for that very reason, and was only changed to permit universal read access to the button box.
      Returns:
      The VBox container housing all selection buttons mapped to all UIBooks in this SidebarBookshelf.
      See Also:
      Sidebar.selectedBookshelfProperty()

    • getButton

      @NotNull public @NotNull javafx.scene.control.Button getButton()

      Returns the Button assigned to this SidebarBookshelf instance.

      Details

      1. When the Button is pressed, the select() method is called on this SidebarBookshelf instance.
      2. Refer to initialize() for Button implementation.
      Returns:
      The Button assigned to this SidebarBookshelf instance.

    • getButtonGroup

      @NotNull public @NotNull BoundImageButtonGroup<UIBook> getButtonGroup()

      Returns the BoundImageButtonGroup responsible for containing and managing the ImageButtons used to switch between selected UIBooks in this SidebarBookshelf.

      Details

      1. The BoundImageButtonGroup returned by this method is used for managing UIBook selection.
      2. The above works because UIBook implements ButtonViewable.
      3. BoundButtonViewGroups add functionality that allows you to retrieve the ButtonViewable (in this case, UIBook) the specified ImageButton is assigned to.
      4. The value returned by this method is guaranteed to be non-null.
      Returns:
      The ImageButtonGroup responsible for containing and managing the ImageButtons used to switch between selected UIBooks in this SidebarBookshelf.
